trans-unit.source: The CmsRecipientCollection class represents a set of <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Klassen CmsRecipientCollection representerar en uppsättning <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: CmsRecipientCollection implements the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> interface.
trans-unit.target: CmsRecipientCollection implementerar den <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>gränssnitt.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The CmsRecipientCollection constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktorn CmsRecipientCollection skapar en instans av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The CmsRecipientCollection constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> class and adds the specified recipient.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktorn CmsRecipientCollection skapar en instans av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> klassen och lägger till den angivna mottagaren.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> class that represents the specified CMS/PKCS #7 recipient.
trans-unit.target: En instans av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"> </xref> klass som representerar den angivna CMS/PKCS #7-mottagaren.

trans-unit.source: The CmsRecipientCollection constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> class and adds recipients based on the specified subject identifier and set of certificates that identify the recipients.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktorn CmsRecipientCollection skapar en instans av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> klassen och lägger till mottagare som baseras på angivna ämne identifierare och uppsättning certifikat som identifierar mottagarna.

trans-unit.source: A member of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SubjectIdentifierType"></xref> enumeration that specifies the type of subject identifier.
trans-unit.target: En medlem i den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SubjectIdentifierType"> </xref> uppräkning som anger vilken typ av ämne identifierare.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Collection"></xref> collection that contains the certificates that identify the recipients.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Collection"> </xref> samling som innehåller de certifikat som identifierar mottagarna.

trans-unit.source: The Add method adds a recipient to the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Add lägger till en mottagare till den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object that represents the recipient to add to the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"> </xref> objekt som representerar mottagaren att lägga till den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: If the method succeeds, the method returns an <xref:System.Int32> value that represents the zero-based position where the recipient is to be inserted.
trans-unit.target: Metoden fungerar om metoden returnerar ett <xref:System.Int32>värde som representerar det nollbaserade plats där mottagaren kan läggas till.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: If the method fails, it throws an exception.
trans-unit.target: Om metoden inte genereras ett undantag.
